reviews.review_text:
Man smart Nice well played and explored versions of these songs.
I like that the Dead started working on the harmonies again.
The Brent tunes really stand out.                                              
(He goes ape-shit in Blow Away)
If you had the chance to see the band from Summer of 88 to those last Tinley Park 90 shows.
It was Mydland who was energizing the band.
